DMGT Seeking Buyer for Its U.S. Trade-Show Unit, GLM, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-06-10T00:51:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-10/dmgt-seeking-buyer-for-its-u-s-trade-show-unit-glm-ft-reports.html
Daily Mail & General Trust Plc (DMGT) ,
publisher of the Daily Mail newspaper, is seeking to sell its
U.S.-based trade-show-management business, GLM, the Financial
Times reported citing an information memorandum sent to
prospective bidders.  The business, which has been looked at by Reed Elsevier
Plc,  United Business Media Ltd. (UBM)  and  Informa Plc (INF) , could be valued
at about $200 million, the FT said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 